data.title: Contact Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada
data.meta_description: Find out how to contact Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada (IRCC).
data.text:
Contact Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada (IRCC)

Find out how to contact IRCC.

Contact the Client Support Centre

Use the web form, get pre-recorded information about our programs or talk to an agent (in Canada only)

Ask about your case or situation

Ask about applications over normal processing times, get application updates or report a technical problem

Check your application status

Get updates with your unique client identifier (UCI), name, date and place of birth

Get help with your eTA application

Get help before you apply or if you have issues when applying for an eTA

Change your address

Change your address, email or phone number
